author: Pollyanna
title: Qualcomm reaffirms it will continue to supply Apple during its legal dispute
text:
By Matthew Lynley 
Qualcomm CEO Steve Mollenkopf said today on the company’s call accompanying its first-quarter earnings report that Qualcomm would continue to work with Apple as a supplier despite a major legal battle happening between the two companies. “We intend to remain a good supplier to Apple even while this dispute continues,” Mollenkopf said on the company’s first-quarter… Read More
